<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exposure-n">exposure <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'spəʊʒə(r)/    美 /ɪk'spoʊʒər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 暴露；显露：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Scientists worry that <strong>exposure to</strong> light while sleeping can increase a person's chances of getting cancer.
科学家们担忧亮着灯睡觉会增加患癌的风险。</p><footer>2013 天津改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2u">2.<strong>[U] 揭露；揭发：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>exposure of</strong> illegal deals
非法交易的揭露</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[常用单数]接触；体验</strong></h4></div>